b. {{Note label|b|b|none}} [https://web.archive.org/web/20051030083152/http://eis.bris.ac.uk/~gexnl/teaching/purism/folkling.html Linguistic Purism in Germany - Folk Linguistics] via the [[Internet Archive]] {{refend}}
